Class JSONArray

    JSONStorageElement<Integer>

    public class JSONArray
extends JSONValue
implements JSONStorageElement<Integer>
    A JSONValue that represents a JSON array.

    This class also extends JSONStorageElement with a parameter type of Integer.

      • getElementsPaired

        public ImmutablePair<LinkedList<String>,LinkedList<JSONValue>> getElementsPaired()
        Returns an ImmutablePair of LinkedLists that hold all of this JSONStorageElement's JSONValue children as well as their corresponding keys/indices.

        This method is particularly useful in transforming a JSON tree back into a Scanner in a single pass. Check out OOJTranslator.JSONValueStreamer for more details.

        Specified by:
        getElementsPaired in interface JSONStorageElement<Integer>
        Returns:
